%META:TOPICINFO{author="LynnwoodBrown" date="1160518180" format="1.1" version="1.6"}%
d10 1
a10 1
%TOPIC% displays  a banner at the topic newly created classification topics. It the basic formatting for the banner, general information and "next step" options. Further help on the particular classification topic is provided by topics specified by the HELP parameter.
d13 1
a13 3
   * HELP - %RED% _Required_ %ENDCOLOR% Specifies the section of this topic that provides any installation or use instructions needed for the new topic.
   * FROM - The topic from which user started in creating a new classification topic.

d21 1
a21 14
<script type="text/javascript" language="JavaScript">
var createTime = "%DBQUERY{"name = '%BASETOPIC%'" web="%BASEWEB%" format="$expand(createdate)" }%";
var currentDate = new Date();

document.write(currentDate.getTime());
document.write("%BR%");
document.write(createTime);

function removeHelp() {
   insertHtml((" "), "newTopicHelp");
}
</script>

%DBQUERY{"name = '%BASETOPIC%'" web="%BASEWEB%" format="$expand(createdate)"}%
d23 2
a24 1
<a href="javascript:removeHelp()">Remove help</a>
d26 1
d30 1
a30 10
